Class SymbolHolder

java.lang.Object
  |

public class SymbolHolder
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This is a holder class that allows Symbols to be serialized and re-constituted. Note that it depends on the Signal values being accessible through hashCode(). Creation date: (2000-03-08 10:46:23)
